{"arkId":"cl010093971","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010093971","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Mercure","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Mercure"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1780","currentLocation":"Abu Dhabi (Emirats Arabes Unis), Louvre Abu Dhabi","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1780,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Pajou, Augustin","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1730","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1809","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q524291"},{"label":"France","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RF 1624","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"statue","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; Sur la plinthe, \u00e0 gauche : \u0022PAJOU, DE PARIS, SCULPT.\/ [ligne martel\u00e9e] \/ 1780\u0022","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"1,96","displayDimension":"1,96 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"0,86","displayDimension":"0,86 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"0,82","displayDimension":"0,82 m","unit":"m","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"marbre","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Command\u00e9 peut-\u00eatre avant juillet 1774 par l\u0027abb\u00e9 Joseph-Marie Terray (1715-1778), directeur des B\u00e2timents du Roi puis contr\u00f4leur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral des Finances, pour la galerie de son h\u00f4tel de la rue Notre-Dame-des-Champs \u00e0 Paris, en pendant de l\u0027Apollon de Mouchy (voir RF 3008). Marbre d\u00e9livr\u00e9 en juin 1774 par le sculpteur Clodion \u00e0 Paris via Marseille (mod\u00e8le au Salon de 1777, n\u00b0 213). Marbre inachev\u00e9 \u00e0 la vente Terray \u00e0 Paris, le 20 janvier 1779, n\u00b0 23 (\u0022la statue... n\u0027est pas enti\u00e8rement finie, et les amateurs pourront en voir le mod\u00e8le dans l\u0027atelier du sculpteur\u0022). Toujours dans l\u0027atelier du sculpteur en juillet 1780. Retir\u00e9 de la vente et rachet\u00e9 par l\u0027h\u00e9ritier de l\u0027abb\u00e9, Antoine-Jean Terray (1750-1794), intendant de Montauban. Plac\u00e9 dans son ch\u00e2teau de la Motte-Tilly o\u00f9 l\u0027\u0153uvre est encore signal\u00e9e en 1818. Collection du baron Basile de Schlichting (1857-1914). Legs de ce dernier, 1915 (comit\u00e9 et conseil exceptionnels du 9 novembre 1914, d\u00e9cret pr\u00e9sidentiel du 13 mars 1915).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Schlichting, Basile de","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"},{"value":"Terray, Antoine-Jean","note":"","role":", Commanditaire"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"13\/03\/1915","startYear":1915,"endYear":1915}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Sculptures du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"legs"}],"material":[{"value":"marbre"}],"objectType":[{"value":"statue"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Gaborit, Jean-Ren\u00e9